The paper deals with session types, which are a formal specification of communication protocols, and introduces a new calculus for unreliable broadcast communication. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Programming Languages (cs.PL), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
